    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Christina Goldbaum</title>
    <description>Christina Goldbaum is an independent journalist and producer based between Nairobi, Kenya, and Mogadishu, Somalia. She has reported across East Africa and the Horn of Africa since 2014, covering issues from regional politics to terrorism and women’s rights. Follow her work at www.christinagoldbaum.com and @cegoldbaum.
</description>
